The primary objective of the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023, is to provide a framework for the **__processing of digital personal data__**. This framework aims to balance the **right of individuals to protect their personal data** with the necessary processing of such data for **lawful purposes**.

**Sources**
*   **[Preamble]** (pdf://DPDP_act.pdf/page/1)
